		<h2 class="story">
				
				
				
			<span id="title-52080095"> <a   href="//hardware.slashdot.org/story/13/10/18/2340206/crossing-the-divide-from-software-dev-to-hardware-dev">Crossing the Divide From Software Dev To Hardware Dev</a></span>
			
			
			<span class="comments commentcnt-52080095" >105</span>
			

                        
		</h2>
		<div class="details" id="details-52080095">
		
		Posted
		by 
	
	
		
			<a href="http://www.monkey.org/~timothy/" rel="nofollow">timothy</a>
		
	
	

	
	
	<time id="fhtime-52080095" datetime="on Friday October 18, 2013 @07:40PM">on Friday October 18, 2013 @07:40PM</time>
	
	
